headline: Why Iron Mountain Stock Rallied 10% in May
summary: Iron Mountain reported strong first-quarter results last month.  The REIT is benefiting from the accelerating growth provided by its growth businesses.  Shares of Iron Mountain (NYSE: IRM) jumped 10.1% in May, according to data provided by S&P Global Market Intelligence.
